Package edu.monash.fit2099.interfaces

Interface ActionInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
Action, AttackAction, BuyAction, DieAction, DoNothingAction, DrinkAction, DropItemAction, EatFromSearchableGroundAction, EatItemOnGroundAction, FeedAction, LayEggAction, MateAction, MoveActorAction, PickUpItemAction, QuitAction, SearchItemAction, ShootAction
public interface ActionInterface
This interface provides the ability to add methods to Action, without modifying code in the engine, or downcasting references in the game.
